{"tid":2057920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又打記者","createTime":"2020-06-09T17:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T00:12:34.000Z","uid":19287,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"74e06d6a498a459ec5dec90379293c57f0f821dd","tid":2057920,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"【6.9 再有區議員被捕】<br />\n<br />\n晚上約11時半，有防暴警員尾隨進入安樂園大廈借用洗手間的年輕女子，引來記者追訪，暴警員見狀召來增援。期間有警員以警棍及手襲擊記者，並以胡椒噴劑指嚇，亦有警員辱罵記者「死狗」，記者向傳媒聯絡投訴並發生口角，「天水連線」天水圍區議員林進在跟進借用洗手間的女子情況時被捕。<br />\n<br />\n採訪期間，本媒記者亦被警員揮拳襲擊頭部，令眼鏡飛脫，圖為辱罵及襲擊記者的警員。<br />\n<br />\n攝 / Joshua Kwan @ USP 社媒特約<br />\n<br />\n#USP #USP20200609 #香港 #hongkong<br />\n<br />\n【新設】USP Instagram account：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/uspunitedsocialpress/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fuspunitedsocialpress%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8bc35274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/uspunitedsocialpress/</a><br />\n【新設】USP Twitter account： <a href=\"https://twitter.com/USPhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSPhongkong&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=acc878a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USPhongkong</a><br />\nUSP Telegram Channel： <a href=\"https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUSP_United_Social_Press&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=72d75f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/579827748716829/posts/3343831312316445/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F579827748716829%2Fposts%2F3343831312316445%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=ad81ba9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/579827748716829/posts/3343831312316445/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"eec98b3